OL,4,CMy emails look ludicrous, says ex-Post
OL,5,COffice PR boss
OL,6,GThe Post Office's former
OL,7,Gcommunications director Mark Davies
OL,8,Ghas admitted that emails he sent
OL,9,Gdenying there were problems with the
OL,10,GHorizon IT system look "ludicrous"
OL,11,Gwith hindsight.
OL,13,FHundreds of sub-postmasters were
OL,14,Fblamed and prosecuted over accounting
OL,15,Ferrors caused by the faulty software.
OL,17,FAt the Post Office inquiry on Tuesday,
OL,18,FMr Davies was shown emails by lawyer
OL,19,FJulian Blake in which he had suggested
OL,20,Fjournalists were "campaigning" against
OL,21,Fthe Post Office.
